Follow the canonical standards in `AGENTS.md` and the plan in `PLAN.md`.

- No magic numbers — use `src/config/constants.ts`. No raw style strings in
  components — use `src/theme/ui.ts`.
- Strict TypeScript/ESLint; no `any`, dead code, silent fallbacks, or
  placeholder/fake code.
- Quality gates must pass and must not be bypassed: `npm run quality`
  (and `npm run quality:ci` for Lighthouse; SEO excluded).
- Update `CHANGELOG.md` and `PLAN.md` with real, verified status only.
- `/caveman` status updates: short, direct, no filler.
